      <title>合氣道進步的秘訣【第0466回】　教導法則的基本技之三：「十字」</title>
      <link>https://kaku-budo.github.io/blog/aikido/tips/part-0401-0500/t-0466-cross-principle/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Jan 2026 19:29:00 +0800</pubDate>
